OOPS - object oriented programming structure/system

->Oops is a programming paradigm/methodology
                       ->paradigm mean a style or way to do work
                       ->oop is also a style or way to work or we can say development

->6 Pillar of oops Are

1) Class
2) Object and Methods
3)Inheritance
4)Polymorphism
5)Abstraction
6)Encapsulation

Types of Inheritance
Single level  A -> B
multilevel    A -> B -> C
Hierarchical  A -> B , A -> C

